<DOCUMENT source-infobase-name="Rules" content-collection-id="NYCrules" source-infobase-title="The Rules of the City of New York" base-output-dir="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\" default-split-level="Chapter" makefile-filename="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\NYCrules.mak" css-stylesheet-href="#!-- #ID=NYCrules_css_id --#" xml-output-dir="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\XML\" css-stylesheet-name="NYCrules_css" makefile-document-depth="2">
	<LEVEL style-name="Chapter" style-name-escaped="Chapter" style-id="0-0-0-477" level-depth="2" toc-section="false">
		<RECORD id="0-0-0-148573" number="114111" version="2810">
			<HEADING>Chapter 3. Referral Source</HEADING>
			<PARA>
				<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-19414" name="T74C003"/>Chapter 3. Referral Source</PARA>
		</RECORD>
		<LEVEL style-name="Subchapter" style-name-escaped="Subchapter" style-id="0-0-0-480" level-depth="3" toc-section="false">
			<LEVEL style-name="Subtitle" style-name-escaped="Subtitle" style-id="0-0-0-15301" level-depth="4" toc-section="false">
				<LEVEL style-name="Part" style-name-escaped="Part" style-id="0-0-0-483" level-depth="5" toc-section="false">
					<LEVEL style-name="Subpart" style-name-escaped="Subpart" style-id="0-0-0-15960" level-depth="6" toc-section="false">
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-148477" number="114112" version="2810">
								<HEADING>§ 3-01 General.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-19416" name="T74C003_3-01"/>§ 3-01 General.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148476" number="114113" version="2811">
									<PARA>The Contractor or Subcontractor may request referral to a Community Hire from a Referral Source approved by the Director for the purposes of meeting the applicable Community Hiring Goal set forth in 74 RCNY <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Jump" destination-name="T74C004" destination-id="0-0-0-19424">Chapter 4</LINK>. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148475" number="114114" version="2816">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 12/24/24, eff. 1/23/25) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-148572" number="114115" version="2810">
								<HEADING>§ 3-02 Network of Referral Sources.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-19418" name="T74C003_3-02"/>§ 3-02 Network of Referral Sources.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148474" number="114116" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>a.<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Directory of Referral Sources.</CHARFORMAT> The Director will maintain and publish on a website maintained or controlled by the City a directory of Referral Sources approved pursuant to this section that perform employment recruitment services or other workforce development services. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148473" number="114117" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>b.<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Criteria.</CHARFORMAT> The factors that the Director may consider when evaluating prospective Referral Sources, include, but are not limited to: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148472" number="114118" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>1.<TAB tab-count="1"/>any pre-existing agreement with an agency for employment recruitment services or other workforce development services; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148471" number="114119" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>2.<TAB tab-count="1"/>current and past experience with workforce development programs or initiatives; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148470" number="114120" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>3.<TAB tab-count="1"/>references, past performance and reliability working with workforce development programs with different legal requirements; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148469" number="114121" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>4.<TAB tab-count="1"/>organization, staffing and operational capability to undertake the services necessary to advance employment of Community Hires; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148468" number="114122" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>5.<TAB tab-count="1"/>relevant experience, operational capability and availability of resources to serve a particular population of Community Hires; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148467" number="114123" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>6.<TAB tab-count="1"/>financial capability, responsibility and availability of appropriate resources for the type and complexity of the services; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148466" number="114124" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>7.<TAB tab-count="1"/>record of compliance with all applicable federal, state, and local laws, regulations, licensing and funding requirements; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148465" number="114125" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>8.<TAB tab-count="1"/>ability to comprehensively address the needs of the Contractors and Subcontractors to meet the Community Hiring Goals; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148464" number="114126" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>9.<TAB tab-count="1"/>ability and reliability to develop quality assurance for monitoring and reviewing performance indicators, including the availability of appropriate technology and resources for data management and quality improvement; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148463" number="114127" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>10.<TAB tab-count="1"/>experience with entering data into multiple data systems and mechanisms and ability to transfer such data to the Director and agencies, upon request; and <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148462" number="114128" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>11.<TAB tab-count="1"/>record of maintaining harmonious labor relations. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148461" number="114129" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>c.<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Determination.</CHARFORMAT> The Director may approve a Referral Source using any of the following methods: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148460" number="114130" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>1.<TAB tab-count="1"/>authorizing one or more entities, as appropriate, to function as Referral Sources based on responses to a publicly released solicitation that includes a description of the functions of a Referral Source, the manner in which responses must be submitted, and the criteria by which the responding entities will be evaluated for approval; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148459" number="114131" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>2.<TAB tab-count="1"/>authorizing an agency, in writing, to function as a Referral Source; or <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148458" number="114132" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>3.<TAB tab-count="1"/>authorizing, in writing, an entity engaged pursuant to an agreement with an agency for employment recruitment services or other workforce development services to function as a Referral Source. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148457" number="114133" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>4.<TAB tab-count="1"/>Notwithstanding the above, the Director will deem any Union Referral System identified in a Project Labor Agreement to be a Referral Source for the purposes of this title. For any Union Referral System that is not identified in a Project Labor Agreement, the Director will deem such Labor Organization to be a Referral Source, in writing, provided that the Labor Organization demonstrates that it has either: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148456" number="114134" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>an affiliated registered apprentice program with direct entry access from at least one pre-apprentice program compliant with United States Department of Labor and New York State Department of Labor regulations; or <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148455" number="114135" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(b)<TAB tab-count="1"/>an affiliated community recruitment program. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148454" number="114136" version="2816">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 12/24/24, eff. 1/23/25) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-148571" number="114137" version="2810">
								<HEADING>§ 3-03 Responsibilities.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-19420" name="T74C003_3-03"/>§ 3-03 Responsibilities.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148453" number="114138" version="2810">
									<PARA>A Referral Source must perform, at minimum, the following responsibilities: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148452" number="114139" version="2811">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>a.<TAB tab-count="1"/>identify individuals who meet the applicable requirements for certification pursuant to 74 RCNY <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Jump" destination-name="T74C002" destination-id="0-0-0-19408">Chapter 2</LINK>; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148451" number="114140" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>b.<TAB tab-count="1"/>assist prospective Community Hires with preparation of self-certification statements for purposes of certification, where applicable; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148450" number="114141" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>c.<TAB tab-count="1"/>maintain, for each Community Hire, the proof of certification and a record of services provided, including, but not limited to employment recruitment; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148449" number="114142" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>d.<TAB tab-count="1"/>provide Contractor, Subcontractor, prospective Contractor or prospective Subcontractor with proof of the individual’s certification as a Community Hire, where applicable; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148448" number="114143" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>e.<TAB tab-count="1"/>establish screening procedures or systems to identify prospective Community Hires; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148447" number="114144" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>f.<TAB tab-count="1"/>provide, without financial costs to the Community Hires, employment recruitment services or other workforce development services; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148446" number="114145" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>g.<TAB tab-count="1"/>enroll in an electronic system designated by the Director; and <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148445" number="114146" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>h.<TAB tab-count="1"/>cooperate in any audit by the Director, including any inspection of documents related to services performed as a Referral Source. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148444" number="114147" version="2816">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 12/24/24, eff. 1/23/25) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-148570" number="114148" version="2810">
								<HEADING>§ 3-04 Performance Review.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-19422" name="T74C003_3-04"/>§ 3-04 Performance Review.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148443" number="114149" version="2810">
									<PARA>The Director will monitor the performance of Referral Sources. The Director may terminate or suspend a Referral Source where the Director has been presented with sufficient information demonstrating any of the following: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148442" number="114150" version="2811">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>a.<TAB tab-count="1"/>inactivity or refusal to perform the responsibilities set forth in 74 RCNY § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Jump" destination-name="T74C003_3-03" destination-id="0-0-0-19420">3-03</LINK> or other workforce development services for a particular population of Community Hires; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148441" number="114151" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>b.<TAB tab-count="1"/>failure or refusal to enroll and maintain an active account in an electronic system designated by the Director; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148440" number="114152" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>c.<TAB tab-count="1"/>fraudulent or bad faith acts; or <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148439" number="114153" version="2810">
									<PARA>
